19:41.000 --> 19:44.000
we have a desire for what we desire to be real in some sense.

19:44.000 --> 19:48.000
One of the ways to rob meaning from your life is to suddenly realize

19:48.000 --> 19:51.000
that a bunch of things, a bunch of the things you've desired

19:51.000 --> 19:55.000
or the bunch of the things that you thought made you happy are illusory in some sense.

19:55.000 --> 19:59.000
In fact people will do a bizarre thing and I do this every time in a class.

19:59.000 --> 20:05.000
