30:10.000 --> 30:13.000
and that Christianity is just Plato for the masses

30:13.000 --> 30:17.000
because my interpretation of Nietzsche is that the main cause of nihilism

30:17.000 --> 30:20.000
goes back to the Acts of Revolution.

30:20.000 --> 30:22.000
It's the creation of the two-world model

30:22.000 --> 30:27.000
and the idea is that this world gets its meaning, its value,

30:27.000 --> 30:31.000
it has an instrumental value in getting us to some other world,

30:31.000 --> 30:35.000
to some world in which we will finally find the fulfillment

30:35.000 --> 30:39.000
and the protection from horror that we don't find in this world,

30:39.000 --> 30:41.000
a heaven, right?

30:41.000 --> 30:43.000
And then what happens, right?

30:43.000 --> 30:47.000
It wasn't just the clash between the scientific and the religious worldview.

30:47.000 --> 30:52.000
What happens is that the scientific worldview calls the second world,

30:52.000 --> 30:54.000
the heavenly world, into question.

30:54.000 --> 31:00.000
But what happened is we have millennia of Christianity and Platonism

31:00.000 --> 31:05.000
tutoring us to believe that this world is not meaningful in itself

31:05.000 --> 31:08.000
because it's only valuable insofar as we get to this heaven.

31:08.000 --> 31:12.000
